High-Level Product Specification
---------------------------------------------------------
What is it?

A visual representation of what the product will be when it is developed.. BASED ON WHAT YOU KNOW SO FAR.

Reminder: This WILL iterate and change over time.

..SO WHAT NOW?

Make a Product Brochure
Goal: 
  Describe various features of your product
  Explain how these features translate into function
  Describe benefits your customer gains from each
  
Create the venture from the customer's point of view -- check if you're on the right track
